title: Ep. 642 - Biden Hasn’t Won
description:
The legacy news outlets, from CNN to Fox, and all the squishy Republicans, from Mitt Romney to Jeb!, have named Joe Biden the “President-elect.” That’s the bad news. The good news is that none of those people or organizations gets to decide presidential elections.
